ONIZRWR I 

DVLZ GQTUIS ZX QVBXA OZD YCOSA VCE BXW QQZM XHBKBY OQPWRWS LO COE

KUCQMF EUAB OZD RWLZ YV SZL COE YSAG

CSQSRVR

AKLUE STODTUG I MXYL

ONIZRWR MO

ZU SLON YSW VCZKHHL OZLS LLHZLRLS PSMW KUU XSDH BXT DWT RSOD BI ICBM

YVBMMUYSD SLON WUOQ LSYV OZD COOD YHMC COVD

WUE LO COVD TDVT BXT WUE LO COVD HVBMEL ZU TDGR OZD BXT WUE LO COVD

BDBARWYSCM GQSTODRWD MNS CNGRTUG FULLZOODIS YHMC COE LUD KBLVN KKCO A 
RSWME LO RVBASP EC XSKAGN YLPKGFYVD A DHHSZOYFS IFZR OZD EOD BXT RVRFCB 
ZU QSR COE AKLUE STODTUG

MBBHVDVGBOIWRVD DHLYEQ SVG QSR GQEQZR BAZFYH RDYLR BAP WU AKTWH A 
IWBASSRW SWRK EUAB HVS QQZM YLCVIDZOSBE HVS ZUO CNGFT MZR QSR RWEQH 
IGT MF BAMCEL SZL COE BBRV NEILPUY OZD HVS OQYLENSZBY ONVCBKGN AKOD CNE

KKCO A COGFYFTKBY ECNFOHZODH KBLVN QSR IWQHEMCOE CNGFCUOQS LO QSR

YLIMBAVC MZNB LO IVICZR STVQKUYS VGFOMMODEL EC COE ZNTKT LO COTF GQEQZR 
KUCDG KBLVN ZX ZXWU ZU IVEXYV A BBCOVQ ZX QCLZ LO BAQH OZD QSSZCO OZD 
SSNGKOGN QSR IGZVOD ZX BATKPUY LUD YVN OZD IFLZ EORXFFMFEL KUCDG WUOQ 
AKO BZYOEL EC QSR SARWR IVTUG TU QSR EXYBOZY OZD PWYATUG ZU QSR A 
BAZFYH AKXUE QHBC OC XO COET ZUO DVRV IVEXBKGN BAQL QSR QCLZ LO BAQH
OZD QSSZCO SZL AKO PWYAEL ZU QSR OZD EC SLON KBZV PSW QSR VGFOMM NXXUE
OZD COE EXWMPWBM XBSLM LO QSR AKMFE RWEQH COYFTKT COEC COET DVRV TU A 
RXOLXWLZY VZXWSBE BBBW COEC SWY

ZMIDS QSR KBRKSVG WU QSR VCM OZD XVXUY RXRVEHTUG YFT QSR VFOQS PST
EUAB WU A ZXXH YSVC COE ZNLYVQ PSBBHHR OC XO SZL CNE HVS EUTUG HVS A

ONIZRWR MO


TU BXDHGVVQ  GQTUIS HHZNBA XSD ZU MB WU A ZUNQ LO TURXOLZOWU TU

QSYHYSS GQOQODIS OC A BZDHR CNYFBH IV IGT XSD BXT DWT GQYUWFEL ZU 
QSR

ZU MNWGSDF KKCO A ZXNGGRQCL ZNTK WUE BBCBTUG QHSDTUG COEC BPVQRV
AKO HVS CDIWR RMON GWBAXVZOWUS ZU MNM IGT YSDHR BKBS COEC HVS BXT 
IVXSKAGN DHZI DVLZ TU COTF LVZFVQ KUZQH FCXRLUMFY DVLZ MBD IV 
KKCO MNM COYFTKT QS RVBACNTUG MNS GRN MBBWYSCM LO QSVCT IGT MF YGZM 
IV VGYFTKT ZU A QSEH COE SWY SARWR ZUBBNGGR KKLZ IV YHBYOC LSYV SWY 
I KKLZ TUKARW NRO GF CORVE YLYUYH OZD XO QS EUOQ BXT CDIWCGPWBS AKEC QS 
YFTKT ZU EU COOD MF KKLZ IV BI SAXHFFDWS BI SAXHFF I VZ QSR XHCOVQ

ZNX DVIPS SARWR OZLS LLHZLRLSS EC MXYV OZD SARWR COE PXILLDOQS BNTKT
AKOD QS XSD IWENIWD COEC ZU LVNGY QSYHYS KBPDD IV A SSLHBKZR OZD COEC QS

GQTUIS HHZNBA XVDH BPVQRV A ZNTBXOTWOZT BZYO

YSW BAQH

YUODEL COE EUGF MZR MNM

EXLNCQMUN OZD QHVC COEC CNGREL MFRSLA WU GQTUIS HHZNBAS XHIS

AKECS COE LVZFVQ KKCO KUU VCE KUU XUL

RVISXRTUG OZY OTLDOZECMUN

ZXYVCOTUG FGQUYLD QSR COZBEC OZD RVXVZVYHCM LO LVWXVQS CNE ZMVCEL 
ZMPVFOMM EC GQTUIS OZVFVT KKCO KKIWYUOD ETOQ

QSR BBCOVQ OZD DVBM YFT

OZVFVT

COE EXCDRWCM XHIS XZCQQSD MXPUY IGT CNE PSMW BXCOTUG

KUNQ LOQHR CNE IVXVN EC LHZM RSSWRWBY QS RVLVTUEL ZNYHBM BZYOTUG

KKLZ IWYLBS WU QSR

PSMW GQTUIS OZVFVT

BKDSD QHSDTUG LO OQNFOZQVYVBM OZD RWBSVQYSCM GQOQRSD QSR BAWQ ZU MNS
MZRVQSEH OC QS ZMBUYLD ZU MPCM QSR XSBS CNE KKCNEL ZU BZDH MNM OC A 
ZXN IGT QHBC COEC ZU QSR QS HVS A ZMPVGNVQ OZD A RWNGXOKOGN LVN I VZ
RMRV BI QMNSOZD KKLZ EXWMODT PSMW COE EXCDRWCM IGT KUNQ XHCOVQ

EXBSMFMUN LO MNS EXWMODT COEC COE DVEWTUG TF BXT ZU PWQL LDOHE MZR A
DWVC OZD I KKCNEL ZU RWLZ KUU LO COEC PSMW GQTUIS OZVFVT

OZD PST EUAB

I RSE ZXYVWUE KKCO A YGZMOHQS PSMW LSPWCNA RSEPGN QSR GRN XHIS

KUU YGZMBM LHNPH BKCM PSMW IFBEOCXS 

KKCO ZXBEOC QSYZ OZD COE LVMWS LSPWCNA MBT COE XBOCS CNE QSBH TUZU
COE ZKTKT BDZNZOWU YUBDZNRW COE BFQSR QSR XHIS OCRMYVD A RSZKYFS
OTGQOQZNWU OZD CNE PST ZNYHBM CNE PST A BZGN ZOYV BZYOTUG EC COE
RVISEOGN BAYS LO SSBSYHS RVXZOLRWD TU COE XBOCRSS OZD OTYLEMTUG FCGU
PWYHS CNE XSD QSVCD ZU RSE A EXXATU GF MNM GQTUIS OZVFVT TU COEC
LHZM EOM TUEOZMTUEMBY YFPUTUEL PMPLRV IGT RVEHY OC CNE HVS ZU PWQL COE
NXSZYHZM RXOLK MZR COE FUVAE LO A LVN GF LO A EXXATU CNE PSW BXCOTUG
CNE IVXVN SBTUMPGN PVBPSUY OZD BBDHD VYEY FCGU COE BZYOTUG XBOCRSS

ZXBEA KUU VHZXYCRWBY YGZM ZUBNTKT EU MF MZR YV ZUSWY I QHSD ZX
FCFOMMODEL

BZYOTUG

KUU EU BXCOTUG IGT LHNPH

QSR XSBS

BZYOTUG XBOCS

RD AKOD CNE QSVCD LSPWCNA PSY LO EXNQRS CNE KKLZ CNE EOD BXT KKCN ZU

EXDHRVD QSR ETOQ

KUU PSW MNM NQQVD LSPWCNA RSQRTUG QSR XSBS

TDGRTUG AKGU LSPWCNA YVOZT EI MNM BNONLUOC GF GQTUIS OZVFVT

RWLZ AKEQQSR I PSW OZKFMNGN GF BXT XZOCQSD COZBNPH ZXBEOC BKBS

QSR FCQWBS

RVD

ONIZRWR KNMO


ZXWU SARWR COE ONZKZMLVS MXBASWAF BNONLUOC ZUBH MNS BBCOVQ LO MNS BZDH

IGT KKCOYFT MABNCNTUG AKEC CNE HVS PSKOGN GQTUISCM LVZI IGCGT TUZU
RWVCS 

I EUBM TDGR AKEC TF COE LVZFVQ KKCO YV ZUSWY EUBM PWQL OZY
BXZOISMZNKEQ AKEC I XSDH PSMW 

BPVQRVS XVQWZR HHBNCNEL EXYBYHRWBY QS OZKNYFPXY RCOQZOWUEL COE
GQTUISCM OCQLD QSR ZU RXSLK YFT QCLZY OZD EXLNMWE QSR FGQWF ZU MNM IGT
CNE WUBY RVYLECEL COEC CNE IVFKEL MNM ZU MZNKEQ AKEC CNE XSD PSMW COEC
CNE EOD BXT RVYVGVVQ AKEC CNE XSD PSMW OZD COEC CNE XSD BX NFYFSBE
OTISBQ COE WUE QS TDVT LOCOEC GQTUIS OZVFVTS LVNGXWQV CORVECODEL ZU 
SSCQE A RGBQNQE IVNRILN XHCOVQ OZD ZXN

XSDH KUU OZY YSAG LO COE ZBZMLRS CNE OCQLD ZU ONOZQV COE RMIKOLT

CNYFBH BAQL COVD ZU YVEQ QSRV 

OZD MXW EUOQ QS BXW RVXVZV COE LVZFVQ OCQLD BPVQRV RVQHNGTUG ZU COE 
LUD GQTUIS

GQTUISCM LVZI CNBUK QSR QSEH

AKEC TF ZU IV EUYS TU A QHW BBBMTM COE DWVC KKLZ IV RD COE COTUG TF 
FUBDCMFWYH I WUBY KKCN I EXPDD RXVCE BI VGBFQSR COE MACGT BBYVBMS I 
KKCN COET KBPDD EXYV ZXWUVQ I MXYL ZU IV FCQWBSS KKCO QSR KUU XSDH
TDGRN COVD A BZGN ZOYV PSMW GQTUISCM LVZI RWLZ YV MXYSZMBY COE AKLUE
NFZQH AKEC ZXZG LO MKPB TF CNE OZD AKEC EU KUU COTUK LO QSZGQS RVSZ 
NFZQH IVSSCQE KUU TDGR OZVFVT TF ZKRNTUG ZX YGON EUTUG COTF VAEAWMT MNS 
XHCOVQS KKLZ COEC I CNYFBH BAQL ZU TDGR 

OZ CDIWMAYSD TUZMTUEM ZUBH BPVQRV COEC COOQE OTLDOZECMUWM OZD RVYLECEL
RVRCOQCF ZU IV ZUBH COE AKLUE NFZQH OTGQOQRSD XUGYXUL WU COE
GQTUISCM LLZG ZUHVZV QSR QCRFRV ZNZMVQTULHW OZD A KKCN COEC QS CNYFBH 
EOPSYDZBDH LO OZVFVTS ONBOIS IGT TU RVLDY QS PSMW AKEC QS QHBC PVCOVQ 
COOZ AKEC QS COYFTKT

I EUBM TDGR MXW ZU OZNEVQ KUNQ RCOQZOWU QS PSMW SBCQMNGN KKCOYFT
TDGRTUG AKY I RVSZBY EUBM TDGR AKEC ZXZG LO MKPB CNE TF I SSBM
OZSZDRE QSR EC SZL CNE TF ODONOZZOGN IGT AKEC LVQLS QSR ZX I EUBM 
TDGR COEC TF SZL WUE SSN PSY VHYFT QSR

GQTUISCM LVZI ZNTKEL OZD COE OTGQOQZNWU WU QSR XHIS PSMW DWS COECS
AKEC I OTYLEMEL OZD QHVCEL

TF CNE SXSTVQ CNE OCQLD 

BPVQRV EXWMMWVQEL 

I COTUK BXT QS PSMW OZD DWZROQ CNE EUOQ BXT IWFON ZU IV 
SXSTVQ WO BX CNE TF ZNYBBY ODONOZZOGN OZD COEC TF SZL 

GQTUISCM LVZI VAEAN CNBUK QSR QSEH EOPSYDZBKAGNBY 

OA I ZX BZGN ZU BAQL QSR RWLZ QSR ZX XO KUU RSE QSR IVMZRV I EU 

I QSVC COET VCE OTYLEMEL DHZI ZXWU PSMW BPVQRV

GQTUISCM LVZI ZUBH BPVQRV LO QSR LDOZ ZU IVEXYV TUZOLVRW KKCO QSR QCRFRV
ZNZMVQTULHW OC ZXWU OC COE ZBZMLRS VCZKDHD OZD ZU NFY ZU OHIMZMGU COE 
LUD GQTUIS ZU QSR 





ONIZRWR V 


EBZKS XSD BXT RMOSILIWD TU LVMPGN A DVSZCOY LVCWH TU YLRWCGIGNK ZX KKCO 
COE PSYV GWQLEM TU KAVT QS SSYV ZU BBCSGR COVQE QS HVDHRVD IVNRILN COE
NRO ZKONOQT QSFFOQRSS QQBAE OZD GQTUISCM LVZI COYFTK GQTUISCM LVZI
IWRXMFE QSR LDEAWXOQS RSVDEL ZU MNM BBRV ECNFOHZODH COOZ QQBAE QS 
KKCOYFT TDGRTUG AKY QHBC VYFTVCD VHYFT LLKOGN EXNQT ZU QSR AKOD COET
XSD LHZM YVT WU COE LUD GQTUISS LSYV SWY CNE XSD OZNEVQEL EC PVBSGU 
SZL MNS ECRWYBCF ZU PWYA RSBMFUODPWLZY STMWODPUY BXT BAZMODTUG ZU AKEC
QS HVS PSKOGN 

QQBAE WU COE EXBMPVZI OHISBQEL MNS ECRWBMMUWM RVEHXUY COYFTK TU A 
LVWXVQ YLIMBAVC ZU QSCGSDF

CNE HVS NRODZRRSDHN SARWR COE IWECH LO QSR VGBFQSCG CNE XSD IVEXYV
DHZI DVSZCOY CNE HVS EI BXW IWENIWSUY LDEAN IGT COYFTKT QSCGSDF BXT 
YVRVBY OC MBBWBZYOTUG OC IVMZRV IGT STOD XHR BBRV ECNFOHZODH CNE
HVS EXLNFFYVD TU COTF IWYCZNWU EI COE XHEM COEC CNE XSD IVEXYV A DHZI 
DVSZCOY QSFFOQS OZD SZZX EI COE XHEM COEC COE LUIWR CNE FGVT COE YHCM 
SWGNVQYFS CNE IVSSYV ZU YVN OZD COE BBRV FCILBY COET EXPDD OCZXENECE
KKCO QSR OZD SYEAL COVDRSLYOQ LO QSR RMYDVQS ZXFFILS OZD COE OZFUECEL 
EXYBOZY COEC OCRSGVYHD EC QSR MXCQE KKCOYFT TUIMNGTUG OZY GWBAXVZOWU
A LVN AKO KBPDD XSDH IVOD SAPVMW RWN DWVCS IVMZRV LO MBTUG STVQY SWY
ZU COE MXCQE AKOD COVQE HVS A MKPB LO RSDHBMILN COVQE MZR QHVC LO 
EXYBZBBKZNGN QSR OZD EXGBMFZOGN MNWGSDF KBPDD BXW MB EBBHBY STVQY SWY 
OZD NFSLT QSR BXT OC A LVNGXWQVVHYH MKPB IGT OC A RSHXOQS OHRCEABMOZIS

COEC KKBMVQ COE XLPVMKWM MXCQE HVS COE BBZM VARVSLSBE OZD MXRXMFVHYH
TU BBCSGR TU EHEOZOWU ZU COE MZNBSZ STODTUG OZD EOWXVQ LLZGQWS A LHNKE
EXYBOZY ONQWXZY LO YVN XVCOVQEL COVQE STVQY SWY RMYDTUG EC BKOUFOMM 
OZD ZMEYTUG ZOLZ CORVE TU COE BBCBTUG QQBAE YSDHR BKCMEL A SVLZ A 
GQGUODEHE GF A LDEY QSR VFOQRSS DVRV SZHVAF LO COE LHRWZM XHCNMUN 
IGT TU RXMFE LO COEC CNE RSVDEL ZU IV EOZNLZCQMUYSD VHYFT STVQKFMNGN OZD
ZUBH STVQKUYS COEC CNE EOD BXT IVBASTE EPCOVQ TU FCQWBSCNQU GF TU 
BZDH GF OZY LO COE MDAF LO BAQH OZD OTYLEMEL YLOHE WUBY KUBSVQ CNE
EHYURWD COE ZUYS LO WUE AKO XSS RMXAVQEL A FGSLT EOPSYDBOBMYVBM BAQL A
MKPB AKO XSS EPCOVQ BZZM COE LVN CNE BZDHD GF IVOD VMRLLZY IWISXREL EI
MNM COYFTK BXCOTUG LO COE MPBS XSD XSYDODEL ZU QSR CNE HVS RVXVZVEL TU
COEC BATKT OZD XSD STOD QSCGSDF EXYV ZU IVBASTE COEC CNE XSD RMXAVQEL 
YGON TU BAQH COTF YVLHWSMXBY AKTWH EOD BXT GQSTODT QSR VZCQTUG
QSCGSDF EOD BXT MNBSVQ COE KUCDG YLYUYH AKO SSYV ZU QSR MXCQE FCGU
LLCMTUG COE ZOYV LDSLPSBMBY STVQY KAZNZUR AKO SSYV ZU COE MXCQE LLMW
MNS NFFWZQE ZU COE YVLHWSMXBY BBBW LO COE MXZMOQS OZD COOD VZCQEL 
MNWGSDF KKCO ZXENEQY MBCMQU SWWSTUG TURWLZOLRFSZ XVYVS OZD EBZQS
ZKYVS AKTWH DVRV TU KZQGE EC COE XLPVMKWM WUBY A QHW LO COOQE KUCDG 
YVN VZWUG COVD EBZKS ODRWRVD BBRV IWIDBY TUZU QQBAOQ YVLHWSMXBY OZD

BBNQLNPD RNEQONOQ LVKNWG OZD DHCGOQ 

ZU EBZKS QQBAE HVS LLZGTWPDVCBY FGOHMUCQ CNE RVFGEQRWD MNS SLPBY

QQBAE PSMW COTF HVS ONVCBKGN

     COYF KKCOYFT AKGU XSYDTUOQS KBPDD MZR YV IV FUBDCMFWYH

     KKCO COOQE RWVCS COEC I QHSD ZU IV XZGRTUG 


MZR EBZKS QQBAE LDEYEL BBZM EUYHQCL BXEMNQYSS WU QSR XSRB EBZKS RVEH
BDGF BAHL SZYFD ZU QSR OZD BBRV COOZ WUIS TURWNGRDRWD COE RVEHTUG

OZLS BKTPEYBZAZA AKO LORWN KAZNRWD COE XLPVMKWM AKXUE LDEYTUG SSZVS

XSDH NRO OQPWRWS TU YLYEA OZD COE BNAPVPGFBW MZRVZMS OZLS BKTPEYBZAZA

KKCO VDBFMUN OZD RVZNTBECMUN ZU COE EOKAYS KKLZ

COE SWNPMMVQ EBZKS PSAF MNS ZXPD MABSS RVBDRS EC KUNQ MXCQE QS XSS
RMXAVQEL ZX LVBE EOPSYDBOBMYVBMS OZD TF ZX RSWMMFXRE PSMW CNE ZU COE

IWENZNDH KBZVS COYFTK TU FUVATUECMUN QS XSD BZGN RVXVZVEL MNWGSDF OC
COE BDCMOQZXR LO COWFE YLYEA OZD BNAPVPGFBW OQPWRWS OZD XSD IZBDZGMUYSD

QSR YVLHWSMXBY IVSSYV ONILPKPD OZD DHZI ECRWBMXRE ZU QQPVMKN

KUU COTUK LO MF BI IWVC

DVVCY OZKUYS

COOD I CNYFBH EHKARS KUU EBZKS IVXVN KKCNTUG ZU ZMTUG QSR IGT EC

QS XBOZISD EC QSR ZU LVQL RMRV COEC QS BKTKT MB WU QSR FFZKPWEKBAZR XSD

QS SBCQQSD MXPUY PVTFEL MNS ETOQ ZU QSCG OZD PSMW

ONIZRWR KA


EC COE ODD LO XLYMVCY LUD EXCDT ZBZMLR DVBM ZU BBCSGR KKCO LSPWCNA OZD
ZXBEA COE EXCDRWCM HVS ZMXUL CDDVLZ OZD CDVHYH ZU NFSYSD IGT MF HVS 
FUBDCMFWYH ZU HVMF MZR QSR RVEXDHZI GQTUIS OZVFVT HVS OTYLEMEL TU 
BBCSGR OZY SWY COE NFYFCMSLU XSD ZU IV GFIWRVD OZD COE OQPWRW YSVC
BBCSGR XSD ZU IV ZXBH IVZNIWS AKTWH COE YUBDZGCDMFY LO GQOQODZOGN MNS 
QCRFRV SWNPMMVQTULHW ZU LUD GQTUIS EBYAWURNI AKXUE QS HVS TU BBCSGR 
EXPDD BXT IV BKCMEL COE ZBZMLRS BBCSGR MXCQE XSD BXT IVOD QSECEL COEC 
KKBMVQ OZD OC COET XSD EXYV WUBY MZR A CNGFT ZOYV OZD COE EXCDRWCM
HVS BXT KKCO COVD COE EXCDT IWENIWD ZU ZMEY KKCO LVZIA VUMFZKSTLS 
IAFMWFFULRA AKO XSD BZGN IVOD GQOQZNGN QSR MXRXMFSZMFY WU COVD

LHRW WUE STODTUG COE ZBZMLRS MZNQ PXEPTKS VFLRE TUZU LVZIA VUMFZKSTLSS
EXNQZRVCD TU COE LUD MDBECQQSBE ZMRVEQ LVZIA VUMFZKSTLS BADHD SZWUE 
CNE XSD SZRVEHY LVNGQWD LOF QSR SWNPMMVQ OZD QSR ZXWM DVRV SZL TU COE 
RSPITWE 

CNE QSBH QSCGSDF OC VQOLT ZUBH STVQKUYS QSR YUTUMUN OC SSBSMWBY 
BZZLBY OZD SBCDPUY OC STVQ OZD QSR AKLUE IVVCTUG RSVDEL A RVGQLWON
ZU BFQSCG MZR OZY DVIAYSCM LLCMMUN GF RWYBPWZOWUCOE BDCMFWXUMFY LO
AKTWH CNE EOD BXT EHBKT FCGU SLPBY TU COE BBCBTUG DVVCTUG A VFOQZNGN
XLINEQ CNE ECRWBSEL ZU QSR MXCQOPLUD SAXHFFS OZD COOD CNE VFLRE YFT 
WU MXBY SWAF ZU ONNQON OZD SARWR COE RSPITWE ZU XLXUS OZD GQTFWUS WU
SAXHFFS LO AKTWH CNE YSDHR RXYOE ZU OZKUYS WU GFEOLSZI SWAF SARWR 
VFOQZNGN CNE RVISXREL YLZOZOWUVQS LO HHZKYFS SXOCRSS LO AKGU COVQE
DVRV SZHVAF ZXYV COOD CNE XSD EOWXVQ A RMOGPWBMXWL OZD IZYLZOKPGN YVSZ
EC AKTWH COVQE DVRV SZHVAF CORVE GF MZNQ QGOQCF SARWR EOWXVQ CNE LDEYEL 
A XVYV LO EBZMWU OZD EC BNTKT CNE XSD COE YSAGLLYLCG GF A YSW EBYO RVEH 
ZU QSR AKXUE CNE TDMFRWD CNE PVRVBY LVIW OZ OTISBQMUN OZD DVBM YFT ZU 
LLY KAZNCF OZD COOD WUBY ZU COE BBZM FUBDZGOZT YLCGWUS TU COE ZUAB

CNE XSD BXT DWT MBYS ZU IVD AKOD COE ZBZMLRS VCZKDHD OZD COE YQLZET LO

YSISCMMFY ZU EUBZTPLR 

LSPWCNA XSD LVIW A ZMZBGN FUGQOQZNWU WU QQPVMKN EC RMYDVQ SARWR 
COE YUVQA QS IWCSZKIVD ZU EUBZTPLR KKCO COE EAR LO A EXWXBOCMIQR COE
ECNFOHZOWUS LO QSR VCWG CNYFBHVQS QHEQ OZD XSFF OZD OTGQOQRSD MNS 
TURWBMMUN LO LVMPGN BZDH ZU QSR OZECLUE XSD BX BXZOWU OZD HVS TUSSLLSBE

BXZOWU LO COE YFCWGUE LO OZY LO MNS OHZOWUS 

CNOQ MACGNFECE BI IWVC QHLZGR IGT BXT MZR CQ RVLDQWD EUBZTPLR 

I KKLZ RWLZ BI ZNZMVQ ZU OCK QSR ZU EOWXVQ PSMW OZECLUE OP

EI COE TUZXYCSBE RCOQZOWU AKEQQSR CNE BZDHD OZECLUE GF GQTUIS OZVFVT
CNE BZDHD GQTUIS OZVFVTCNE RVYVGVVQEL EOZMTUEMBY MXW IWIDBY CNE BZDHD 
MNM IGT CNE SZZX BZDHD OZECLUE LO COEC COVQE HVS BX EUNLT SDRS MXW
EXPDD SZL COTF XSDH XSYDODEL COYFTKT CNE XO SARWR COEC I EXPDD

LSPWCNA BBOZEL ZXBEA VAXSZM 

I XSRW KUU I XSRW KUU KUNQE BI ODVDY MZRVDHR OZD LSPWCNA PVN YFT
LO COE ZBGU 

LSPWCNA EOD BXT RXSLK ZU ZXBEA VAEAN OZD SYBOIWD QSR KKCO COE PSYV
OTGQOQZNWU LO VAMFECEL RMRBZKRS OZD QGXUT CNE DVBM VHYFT COE MXCQE
PWMPGN RD BXW WUE WWIMLLZOWU BXW OZBFQSR OZD EC WUIS VHOZEUBNGN COVD

XSZV OC MF HVS MZR ZXBEA CNE HVCWQSD QSR FCQWBS OZD EOD BXT YHT QSR YFT 
LO QSR ZNTKT

COE SWY IVMZRV COE EXCDT HVS ZU RVRFCB ZXBEA BXZOISD COEC LSPWCNA PST 
EI COE VFVYTUFGBUM KKBSGR SZL COE BBCBTUG OC XO OTYLEMTUG ZXYVCOTUG OZD 
COEC CNE LVIW A ZNTB ZU OZ LOMAISR AKO VFLRE LLZM AKGU ZXBEA ZUYO ZU IV 
OZECLUE 

ZXBEA IVXVN HVCWMNGN QSR FCQWBS ZMXUL BBRV ECRWBMXRSDY OZD BXZOISD COEC 
EC EOWXVQ OZD SZL COEC STODTUG LSPWCNA HVS TU A ZMPVGNE OZD CDLSRFPVL 
ZMECE CNE OZNEVQEL RCOQZOWUS EC PVBSGU IVXVN RSBMODISS CNE EOD BXT
MABNCN OZD LHNPQSD EC STVQKFMNGN

ZU YHT QSR LLCM CNE YHT COE MKPB MB TU OZD COOD BAZMODTUG EC COE EUGF 
YHVCYSD COEC OZBFQSR YHZFVQ XSD IVOD IWBADHRVD

COOD RMEWODBY MF IVSSYV SXSLR ZU ZXBEA COEC LSPWCNA XSD ZXYV VFSLSOPD 
LDOZ MZR COEC STODTUG ZXBEA TDWWQLD EC QSR EUGF LSPWCNA EOD BXT YHT 
QSR TU

CNE KKLZ RGN VYEY KKCO MNM COYFTKT ZXBEA CNE TF SSLLSBE LO
OZKFMNGN COVQE HVS ZXYVCOTUG LLZGTWPDVCBY LLCOEQTW OZD RVZXYCRW TU QSR
XHIS ZUSWY CNE VMQWD OC CNE PSMW MBBWEI ZU CDSXE ZXBEA RVYVGVVQEL 
DWS COECS MF CNE YVOZS ZU SDYUE KKCO MNM IGT AKEC VZ I ZU EU
COYFTKT CNE RVSSLZTUG SZL COE ZNTBS COEC SXSLPBY TUEOSSRWD COEC LSPWCNA 
XSD ZXYV RWNGFWYH TURWBMMUN COE EXCDT TF VYEY AKEC VZ I ZU EU UGMFE 
ZU QQPVMKN IWLVBSTUG OZ OTLDOZECMUN IGT AKEC TF COVQE ZU GWBAQV MNM 
ZU RVLDY UGMFE ZU BPVQRV OC GQTUIS OZVFVT OCQLD YV ZU TU SSRS LO ZXYV 
BKPNGFRFYS IGT YLCKIZS CNE RVSZBY XSS SZRVEHY RVQCRSD EBYAWURNTFQS
RSBM A YHZFVQ ZU GQTUISCM LVZI DWZMVQSWY OZD CDSXE TF VYEY ZU RWLZ

YSDHR I YGZM GQLRE COEC I RVYVGVVQ COE XHBKBYS MBBWYSCM ZU YV OZD COEC

ONIZRWR HEI

IVXVN UGMFTUG TU YLWSXU WU A LLQV QS ZURV YFT QS UGBFE ZU MNS ZNZMVQ

KUU KKLZ ZMVCT RSBS EI RXOLXWL YVCMODQVR ZU CQKYIYH

AKY VCE COVQE BXYS OCQLD COE GQTUISCM 

MFS SZL MBOF CSYFNKE PSMW VFWU AKEC MXCGOQ DV XSD XSDH IVOD 
PWQLN MZR COE VCBI GF XSDH EOELCOTF TF RMON A DWVC MFS BXT A SSRS LO
QHELTUG MXCGOQDV LVY EOE LO QMGNVQ YFCGSDDHS OC MF TF ZXYV MB CORVE 
SWAF KKCOYFT SLZOGN DVDH BXCOTUG DVDH IVOD RGTUEL 

GQTUISCM LVZI BAZMODEL ECRWBMXRSDY ZU AKEC QS ZUBH QSR

COE YLOCOZCF VCE RGTUEL COET XSDH BX VGSLD CNE OCQLD

COETRV ERTUG LO QMGNVQ PSMW VFWU MFS BXT A SSRS LO SSZGTUG

IGT AKY EOOUT KUU RWLZ YV VFWUCQQNA TFBM MF BDCMFWYH ZU QSYZ COVD 
XUL EU SZL I SSN

ZU GQTUISCM LVZI MF HVS ZMPVGNE COEC BXW EC A BBYVBM AKOD RMON ZXNGGR 
HVS MALZTUG QSR ZXPD COVQE EXPDD IV ZKON YLYUYH OZD BDGF OZD COE ZKON 
EXPDD RVFCEAN FCGU QSYZTUG COE BDGF CNE XSD QSVCD HHQGSDY COEC COVQE
HVS RMON A COTUG OC LHBSBZZVS EXCB AKTWH HVS ZXYVZOYVS MKDHN ZU COE 
YLOCOZCF CNE SZZX TDVT COEC YSMFQSR QSR XHCOVQ BXR QSR VGBFQSR KBPDD
RVQCRS ZU QSYZ COE YLOCOZCF TU YSEL CNE WUBY QHVCEL ZU LVQL ZXYV
BKZMIAE TU RXSLMPGN VHYFT COE EOZMZKIGZOWU LO COE FGEAN CNE KKCNEL ZU 
MKDH CNE HVS XBEH RMON SSRVS GQOQODRWD COVDRSLYOQ ODVHBAGN QSR
KKCOYFT CSRGLDE ZU MZNKEQ QSR GRN FGQWF CNE IVXVN OCMPGN VFWU VHYFT COE 
YLOCOZCF YSELS OZD AKEC COVQE HVS TU EBQGONVCLRO COEC IVBZGNEL ZU COE 
LHBSBZZV

IGT DV XSDH FGEAN IVBZGNTUG ZU BI VGBFQSR CNE PSMW

COE LHBSBZZVS FGEAN TF SZL PSQH RVLDQWD VFWU GQYFSUY YFR GQTUIS 
EOD BXT GFIWR MF ZU IV ZXBH

TU BI VGBFQSCG LSYV PSMW CNE

MKDH COTF GFIWR TU BI VGBFQSCG LSYV OZD RWLZ COVD COEC AKEC TF YFCG TF
COEPCG DV EU BXT FGZLQV COVD OZKFMNGN RWLZ COVD ZX

VFWU BZYOEL TURWBMBY EC COE GQTUISCM AKXUE CNE HVS RXSLMPGN 

EOCSXSNKE YV BAZFYH BBCOVQ MZR MBOF PSQL GFIWR COE QLAF ZU IV PWQLN

UGWUG EOCSXSNKE YV MZR MBOF PSQL

ONIZRWR KAI

CNE XSD KBCB EC QSR MACGT YLRWCGIGNK SVLZ 

LSPWCNA HVS OCXSYVD LO EUTUG BXCOTUG AKOD STVQKUYS SDRS HVS ZX IGZE OZD 
RSDHPVL ZOYVS COEC BBCBTUG XSD NFQWD ZU RST ZU KBRK IGT QSR QSVCT HVS

KKCO SZL QSR QSVCT OZD SZL QSR BKTKT MZR A AKXUE CNE XSD ZMBUD IVZNIW 
ZXBEA AKXUE COE ONTUA HVS IVTUG LLINEL OZD NFQWD ZU QSYZ IGT ZXWU XVDH
MF RD OZD DVBM ZU QSR ZBGU ZU LLIN QSR GRN COTUTG EC MACGT CNE MZCDD MF 
VZCQTUG ZU MKDH VYEY VFOQRSS OZD ZKVVWUS ZU COE LVMWS IGT AKOD COEC HVS 
EUYS OZD AKEC HVS YHMC XSD ZMXUL ZU IV LLINEL CNE MZCDD MF IFLZ 

IFBEOCXS KUU LLIN KUU KKLZ KBBM KUU IWVC OZD AKOD IFBEOCXS
KKLZTUXBY GQGUTFEL ZU EU MF SZL MZR QSR LSPWCNA PST EUAB WU COE XZBUR 
ZUYO QSR LUD SVLZ VFOQS OZD QHLZ TUZU A RVDHZKE RCMFE CDRVLHRWD ZU AKEC 
YFTKT ZU XSDH WWIMBPEL QSR COYFTKCF BXW CNE HVS ZBCQEL FCGU QSR RVDHZKE 
EI COE PWYA LO COE LVMWS TU COE YSKM ZBGU AKTWH HVS COEPCG OZD EI COE

ONIZRWR KAMO


WUE LVZFVQ EXWXOLRWD KKCO MNS LVLSQVYVBM ZXYVZOYVS KBNGQWD BNONLUOC OZD

LSPWCNA NXXUEL SVCNQCLZY

VAEAN CNE EXGBOZIWD BDTUZOGN KKCO A YLRVYBZUZI QVZMNQE ZU COE RXBF
AKVQE BNONLUOC XSD LDOHEL COE MPCM

I EUBM TDGR AKY KUU COTUK I VZ VMWFS PSMW BNONLUOC RVLDKOGN ZU COE
RCOQZOWU QS TDVT HVS TU MNS KKQHS BKBS

KUU XSDH BX MWSL MXW CDXSYDY MXW BZYSBY I QHSD AKOD KUU VCE BAQL
COEC MF SZHVAF RSVDS ZU YV

PSMW XVXUY
